  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 37-28-33, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROVIDE THAT THE CHARTER OF A CHARTER SCHOOL SHALL BE REVOKED OR NOT RENEWED FOR ANY SCHOOL THAT IS DESIGNATED A \"D\" OR \"F\" RATED SCHOOL UNDER THE SCHOOL ACCREDITATION RATING SYSTEM FOR LONGER THAN TWO CONSECUTIVE YEARS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
